{"tid":234303,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"母親節只係資本家騎劫母愛嘅產物","createTime":"2017-05-08T08:03:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T08:48:32.000Z","uid":94742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1def7146eb6e106830fa405c65a6388dafb4e27","tid":234303,"uid":94742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:03:24.000Z","msg":"點解母親節一定要慶祝、要買禮物、要食飯？<br />\n如果真係感情好～ 根本唔洗等母親節都會做哩堆野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n母親節就係迫d唔想做哩堆野嘅人迫住做，迫佢地有回饋母愛嘅需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同時迫本身會做哩堆野嘅人額外又例牌地做多次！！保證為人囝囡一定要洗錢⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無諗過有d人死左母親，會勾起人傷心回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無諗過有d人由細比母親虐待，母親節只會令佢離不開痛苦陰霾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有d母親明明對仔女好衰，但又奉旨覺得母親節要仔女同佢慶祝～ 又要攞其他真係快快樂樂成長家庭比較<br />\n如果唔慶祝就日日比人煩，慶祝又好似做戲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行出街周圍商品都分分秒秒提醒你要慶祝母親節<br />\n好恐怖好痛苦呀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24d7975ffaaa5425746562ab6c1f3e9123a01b2","tid":234303,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:11:28.000Z","msg":"不孝子就係等呢一日post上facebbok呃like"},{"pid":"7afc377a11c06ee6494d2dbd29dd34a5b6aeac8d","tid":234303,"uid":114915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T08:48:32.000Z","msg":"Living without an aim is like sailing without a compass"}]}